    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>CANADA WEIGHS SANCTIONS</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Elizabeth Olson</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Olson, Elizabeth</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>World Trade Organization rules that Canada may impose up to $157 million in sanctions over six-year period against Brazil to punish country for illegally subsidizing jet airline industry (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Canada may impose up to $233 million ($157 million) in sanctions over a six-year period against Brazil to punish the country for illegally subsidizing its jet airline industry, the World Trade Organization says. The size of the sanctions may fall if the two countries settle.</p>
        <p>Elizabeth Olson</p>
      </block>
